'''Dread Pirate''' was an honorific given to legendary [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]]. One known holder of the title was the infamous [[Mendel Cutter]], who commandeered the ''[[Rusted Cutlass]]'', settled down at [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']].

